{
  "stem": "3206.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came there, and there was [NON-ENGLISH] for the President, you know, Joseph Stalin-- not Joseph Stalin, Jozef Pilsudski This was very good for the Jews in Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there was a whole celebration, the third of May.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they all came to that shul, and this was a beautiful shul.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was going, like, practically every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I was 13 years-- I still remember-- when I was bar mitzvahed, it was 1939.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were already in Poland. 1939, my father took me into that [NON-ENGLISH], and they gave me aliyah, and this was my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they told me, from now on, you're on your own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You have to put tefillin and tallis every morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You have to be a good Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This is what I remember-- 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then my mother died the same-- the same time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she was buried in Staszow in that cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was also 1939, and I still remember I was saying Kaddish practically the whole year, till 1940. 1940, they took me away from Staszow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who had in mind even to think about politics?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only struggle which was there-- to make a living, to make barely to go by every day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was the main struggle at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like I just described you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, like, we had a gymnasium in-- in Staszow-- very nice, higher education. like, when you finished school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were 13 years old when you finished school-- seven grades.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when you had the means, you want to go for higher education.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was called gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
